= Topic Assessment Overview

#info-box[
  *Assessment Details:*
  - *Total Questions:* 20
  - *Time Limit:* 40 minutes (strictly timed)
  - *Average Pace:* 2 minutes per question
  - *Topic:* Number Properties & Arithmetic
  - *Conducted In:* Lesson C
  - *Purpose:* Determine mastery before advancing to next topic
]

#warning-box[
  *Assessment Conditions:*
  1. No notes, calculators, or outside resources
  2. Timer must be visible
  3. No pausing allowed
  4. All questions must be attempted
  5. Cannot return to previous questions (simulates GMAT)
]

